---
// Rooms.astro — Magazine spread editorial, NOT card grid
---
<section class="rooms" id="rooms">
  <div class="rooms__header reveal">
    <span class="label">The Rooms</span>
    <h2 class="headline rooms__title">Crafted for<br /><em>stillness</em></h2>
  </div>

  <!-- Room 01 — Full bleed left, content right -->
  <div class="rooms__feature rooms__feature--left">
    <div class="rooms__feature-media">
      <img
        src="/images/rooms-cozy-interior.jpg"
        alt="The Canopy Suite — second floor, forest view"
      />
      <span class="rooms__feature-num">01</span>
    </div>
    <div class="rooms__feature-content">
      <span class="label rooms__label">The Canopy Suite</span>
      <h3 class="rooms__name">Second Floor · Forest View</h3>
      <p class="rooms__desc">
        A king bed oriented toward the eastern canopy, where morning light filters through
        Sitka spruce at first hour. Hand-hewn cedar beams overhead, a soaking tub positioned
        beneath a window that has never known a curtain.
      </p>
      <div class="rooms__details">
        <div class="rooms__detail">
          <span class="rooms__detail-label">Size</span>
          <span class="rooms__detail-val">680 ft²</span>
        </div>
        <div class="rooms__detail">
          <span class="rooms__detail-label">Bed</span>
          <span class="rooms__detail-val">King, Edmunds &amp; Myers</span>
        </div>
        <div class="rooms__detail">
          <span class="rooms__detail-label">View</span>
          <span class="rooms__detail-val">Old-growth canopy, east</span>
        </div>
        <div class="rooms__detail">
          <span class="rooms__detail-label">Tub</span>
          <span class="rooms__detail-val">Copper soaking, floor-level</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <a href="#reserve" class="btn btn--outline rooms__btn">Inquire</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Room 02 — Content left, full bleed right -->
  <div class="rooms__feature rooms__feature--right">
    <div class="rooms__feature-content rooms__feature-content--right">
      <span class="label rooms__label">The Bark Room</span>
      <h3 class="rooms__name">Ground Level · Garden Edge</h3>
      <p class="rooms__desc">
        Named for the contractor who refused to sand any of the reclaimed fir beams.
        "The texture is the story," he said. A private garden terrace faces south toward
        a meadow that turns gold every August without anyone's help.
      </p>
      <div class="rooms__details">
        <div class="rooms__detail">
          <span class="rooms__detail-label">Size</span>
          <span class="rooms__detail-val">540 ft²</span>
        </div>
        <div class="rooms__detail">
          <span class="rooms__detail-label">Bed</span>
          <span class="rooms__detail-val">Queen, West Elm</span>
        </div>
        <div class="rooms__detail">
          <span class="rooms__detail-label">Terrace</span>
          <span class="rooms__detail-val">Private, 220 ft²</span>
        </div>
        <div class="rooms__detail">
          <span class="rooms__detail-label">Bath</span>
          <span class="rooms__detail-val">Rainfall shower, slate floor</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <a href="#reserve" class="btn btn--outline rooms__btn">Inquire</a>
    </div>
    <div class="rooms__feature-media">
      <img
        src="/images/rooms-soaking-tub.jpg"
        alt="The Bark Room — garden terrace, afternoon light"
      />
      <span class="rooms__feature-num">02</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Room 03 — Cinematic horizontal -->
  <div class="rooms__horizontal">
    <div class="rooms__horizontal-media">
      <img
        src="/images/rooms-cabin-greatroom.jpg"
        alt="The Ember Loft — mezzanine suite, wood stove"
      />
    </div>
    <div class="rooms__horizontal-content">
      <span class="rooms__feature-num">03</span>
      <span class="label rooms__label">The Ember Loft</span>
      <h3 class="rooms__name">Mezzanine Suite · Wood Stove</h3>
      <p class="rooms__desc">
        Accessed by a ladder of recycled hickory, this loft sits in the upper canopy
        where the building meets the treetops. A masonry heater burns oak overnight —
        one load at dusk, embers until dawn. The porch faces west where storms arrive
        in slow motion and the sky turns the color of dark honey.
      </p>
      <div class="rooms__details rooms__details--inline">
        <div class="rooms__detail">
          <span class="rooms__detail-label">Size</span>
          <span class="rooms__detail-val">820 ft²</span>
        </div>
        <div class="rooms__detail">
          <span class="rooms__detail-label">Heating</span>
          <span class="rooms__detail-val">Masonry wood stove</span>
        </div>
        <div class="rooms__detail">
          <span class="rooms__detail-label">Porch</span>
          <span class="rooms__detail-val">West-facing, canopy level</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <a href="#reserve" class="btn btn--outline rooms__btn">Inquire</a>
    </div>
  </div>

</section>

<style>
.rooms {
  background: var(--cream-dark);
  padding: var(--space-2xl) 0;
}

.rooms__header {
  max-width: 1200px;
  margin: 0 auto 6rem;
  padding: 0 2rem;
}

.rooms__title {
  margin-top: 1rem;
  color: var(--ink);
}

.rooms__title em {
  font-style: italic;
  color: var(--green);
}

/* Feature row */
.rooms__feature {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 0.9fr;
  min-height: 600px;
  margin-bottom: 6rem;
}

.rooms__feature--left {
  direction: ltr;
}

.rooms__feature--right {
  direction: rtl;
}

.rooms__feature--right > * {
  direction: rtl;
}

.rooms__feature-media {
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.rooms__feature-media img {
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  object-fit: cover;
  transition: transform 0.8s var(--ease-spring);
}

.rooms__feature:hover .rooms__feature-media img {
  transform: scale(1.04);
}

.rooms__feature-num {
  position: absolute;
  bottom: 1.5rem;
  left: 1.5rem;
  font-family: var(--serif);
  font-size: 4rem;
  font-weight: 300;
  color: rgba(248,245,240,0.3);
  line-height: 1;
  z-index: 2;
}

.rooms__feature-content {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  justify-content: center;
  padding: 4rem 3.5rem;
  background: var(--cream);
}

.rooms__feature-content--right {
  padding: 4rem 3.5rem 4rem 4rem;
}

.rooms__label {
  margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
}

.rooms__name {
  font-family: var(--serif);
  font-size: 1.8rem;
  font-weight: 400;
  color: var(--ink);
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  line-height: 1.2;
}

.rooms__desc {
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  color: var(--ink-light);
  line-height: 1.8;
  margin-bottom: 2rem;
}

.rooms__details {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 1rem 1.5rem;
  margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  padding-top: 1.5rem;
  border-top: 1px solid rgba(74,93,74,0.12);
}

.rooms__details--inline {
  display: flex;
  gap: 3rem;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
}

.rooms__detail {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 0.25rem;
}

.rooms__detail-label {
  font-size: 0.65rem;
  font-weight: 500;
  letter-spacing: 0.15em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--green-mid);
}

.rooms__detail-val {
  font-family: var(--serif);
  font-size: 0.95rem;
  color: var(--ink);
}

.rooms__btn {
  align-self: flex-start;
}

/* Horizontal feature */
.rooms__horizontal {
  max-width: 1400px;
  margin: 0 auto 0;
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1.6fr 1fr;
  min-height: 580px;
}

.rooms__horizontal-media {
  overflow: hidden;
}

.rooms__horizontal-media img {
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  object-fit: cover;
  transition: transform 0.8s var(--ease-spring);
}

.rooms__horizontal:hover .rooms__horizontal-media img {
  transform: scale(1.04);
}

.rooms__horizontal-content {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  justify-content: center;
  padding: 4rem;
  background: var(--green-dark);
  color: var(--cream);
}

.rooms__horizontal-content .rooms__label {
  color: var(--amber-light);
}

.rooms__horizontal-content .rooms__name {
  color: var(--cream);
}

.rooms__horizontal-content .rooms__desc {
  color: rgba(248,245,240,0.75);
}

.rooms__horizontal-content .rooms__detail-label {
  color: var(--amber);
}

.rooms__horizontal-content .rooms__detail-val {
  color: var(--cream);
}

.rooms__horizontal-content .btn--outline {
  border-color: rgba(248,245,240,0.4);
  color: var(--cream);
}

.rooms__horizontal-content .btn--outline:hover {
  background: var(--cream);
  color: var(--green-dark);
}

@media (max-width: 1024px) {
  .rooms__feature {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    direction: ltr !important;
  }

  .rooms__feature-media {
    min-height: 400px;
  }

  .rooms__feature-content {
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
  }

  .rooms__feature-content--right {
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
  }

  .rooms__horizontal {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }

  .rooms__horizontal-media {
    min-height: 380px;
  }

  .rooms__horizontal-content {
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
  }
}
</style>